Surf_supermario
Map by DrSilence (doktorsilencer@googlemail.com)

This map is a bit of an aquired taste. 
You will start in DEV enviroment and will more and more become in Mario64 style.
There are lots of secrets inside the map. I'll hope you can find them all and have fun playing this map.

Map designed for 66 tick, will work with 100.

If you want to modify this map, ask me in a polite email or pm on mapping-tutorials.de.

Visit solidsurf.info for quality surf players and mappers.
visit mapping-tutorials.de for information of mapping.

Have fun surfing.
